{"tid":991804,"cid":21,"subCid":3,"title":"(不能只有我中意)松任谷由実唔只得宮崎駿啲主題曲好聽  出道47年好歌多不勝數","createTime":"2019-01-22T16:01:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-28T13:12:59.000Z","uid":221265,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"422479aef0fcc6d5fd14bffbd3e89836888f53bc","tid":991804,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T16:01:58.000Z","msg":"松任谷由実(YUMING)喺香港，佢知名度遠不及中島美雪，最多人識都係宮崎駿電影《風起了》主題曲〈ひこうき雲〉同《魔女宅急便》嘅〈やさしさに包まれたなら〉。 呢兩首其實都係70年代初佢嘅名曲。 <br />\n<br />\n佢72年出道到依家(嫁前叫荒井由実 )，一直堅持全部歌曲詞自作，編曲就交由老公松任谷正隆做，係日本首席新音樂女王。 70年代到依家都有hit歌，70,80,90,00,10年代都有大碟上到oricon冠軍，喺日本得佢一個5個年代都有大碟冠軍，亦係最年長得到oricon大碟周榜冠軍嘅女歌手(64歲零3個月).<br />\n<br />\n佢亦係日本出名嘅戀愛教祖，歌詞影響好幾代人， 演唱會出名華麗多嘢睇。 <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好覺得佢係阿婆樣衰或把聲怪就覺得佢無料到</span></strong>，今年紅白 佢同桑田佳祐跳辣身舞嘅壓軸又變咗經典同埋當晚收視冠軍啦。 <br />\n<br />\n先po幾首早期70年代作，其實佢80,90年代好多大熱作，00,10年都有冠軍大碟作<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">Velvet Easter ベルベット・イースター</span> (1973)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fkuOaugShsk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DfkuOaugShsk&d=u8%2Bqoai3bpL%2Fx%2BgE41AThF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=60e4ad40\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fkuOaugShsk</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">あの日に帰りたい</span>(1975)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=36d-SKvLh4o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D36d-SKvLh4o&d=u8%2Bqoai3bpL%2Fx%2BgE41AThF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=ce03c395\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=36d-SKvLh4o</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">卒業写真</span>(1975)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uphr3A4vpoU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Duphr3A4vpoU&d=u8%2Bqoai3bpL%2Fx%2BgE41AThF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=fa811169\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uphr3A4vpoU</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">晩夏（ひとりの季節）</span>(1976)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=c_Zl94NkS_8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dc_Zl94NkS_8&d=u8%2Bqoai3bpL%2Fx%2BgE41AThF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=2b7c8cc1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=c_Zl94NkS_8</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">紅雀</span>(1978)婚後首張大碟，由荒井由実改叫松任谷由実<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=T1AMJBHFLrs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DT1AMJBHFLrs&d=u8%2Bqoai3bpL%2Fx%2BgE41AThF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=b32e8dc5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=T1AMJBHFLrs</a>"},{"pid":"6844bb6156f63b9899127e8166e7790e1af3c8c2","tid":991804,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T16:08:46.000Z","msg":"個樣係<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eSMSwcu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeSMSwcu.jpg&h=33dbbf6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DegnTqQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDegnTqQ.jpg&h=8eb49f3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jngjbcv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJngjbcv.jpg&h=0657f55c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d1cKnja.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd1cKnja.jpg&h=aaa73fcf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔開胃<br />\n但歌真心好"},{"pid":"32a887cb3d61beb497d2122bb1d5d276e9f03e21","tid":991804,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T16:19:00.000Z","msg":"haha 果然無人回"},{"pid":"399b96c9ecc966ba554f61039b9912c1a72788b5","tid":991804,"uid":3936,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T16:21:42.000Z","msg":"恋人がサンタクロース<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n留意左樓主好耐<br 